{
  "chapter": 68,
  "chapter_summary": "寇仲与徐子陵驾船运送私盐西行，途中遭遇东海三义高占道、牛奉义、查杰率领的海盗拦截。寇仲以雷霆一刀震慑高占道，双方化敌为友。原来高占道等人本为隋兵，征高丽失败后家破人亡，被迫落草为寇，聚众二百余人盘踞常熟。席间寇仲纵论天下大势，指出李密虽声势浩大，却因杀害翟让导致瓦岗军内部离心，实为致命失误。高占道等人深为寇仲的才识气度所折服。本章展现了寇仲卓越的御人之术和争雄天下的雄心壮志，也为后续收编东海帮埋下伏笔。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "我们试试由大江逆流西行入内陆，如若不行，才再走陆路吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 7,
      "line_end": 9
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "我和你都是操舟的低手，连个普通的船夫都比不上，在大海还没有问题，当然！这只是指风平浪静的情况下而言，若进入河里……",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 11,
      "line_end": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "想那么多干吗？船若在大江沉了，我们就去捞他娘的上来，那时改走陆路也不迟。别忘了我们同是水陆两路的高手。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 15,
      "line_end": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "该轮到你了，我要入舱睡觉。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 19,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "早知抓起几个海沙帮的小儿，逼他们驾船，那现在就不用捱苦了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 23,
      "line_end": 25
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "究是何方神圣？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 35,
      "line_end": 35
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "只听鼓音，便知他们斗志高昂，但看他们行动的散乱无章，更知只是乌合之众，他们定是随处掠夺的海盗，最适合拿来当水手。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 37,
      "line_end": 39
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "甚么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 41,
      "line_end": 41
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "一切由我来应付，现在先往舱内躲躲箭矢，待他们登船才显点手段给这些毛贼看看。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 43,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_zhan_dao",
      "speaker_name": "高占道",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "儿郎进舱这么久了，为何还不见把那两个小子押出来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 59,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_feng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "牛奉义",
      "listener": "char_gao_zhan_dao",
      "text": "让我去看看！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 63,
      "line_end": 63
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zha_jie",
      "speaker_name": "查杰",
      "listener": "char_niu_feng_yi",
      "text": "我陪二哥去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 67,
      "line_end": 67
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_zhan_dao",
      "speaker_name": "高占道",
      "listener": "char_zha_jie",
      "text": "有点邪门，小心点！",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 69,
      "line_end": 69
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zha_jie",
      "speaker_name": "查杰",
      "listener": "char_gao_zhan_dao",
      "text": "我们东海三义甚么风浪未见过。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 71,
      "line_end": 71
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_dao_shou_xia",
      "speaker_name": "海盗手下",
      "listener": "char_gao_zhan_dao",
      "text": "大爷！甲板堆的全是盐货。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 73,
      "line_end": 75
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_zhan_dao",
      "speaker_name": "高占道",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "真倒霉，这些废物除非运往内陆，否则能卖多少钱！不过这艘船倒是上等货色。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 77,
      "line_end": 79
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_gao_zhan_dao",
      "text": "你们那三艘也不错，大概可让我们狠狠的捞他娘一笔。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 81,
      "line_end": 83
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_zhan_dao",
      "speaker_name": "高占道",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你将他们怎样了？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 91,
      "line_end": 91
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_gao_zhan_dao",
      "text": "你先吩咐手下勿要轻举妄动，本少爷才有兴趣研究应否答你的问题。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 93,
      "line_end": 95
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_zhan_dao",
      "speaker_name": "高占道",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "全部人停手，都到我这边来。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 97,
      "line_end": 97
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_zhan_dao",
      "speaker_name": "高占道",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "今趟算我们得罪了。只要阁下放人，我们立即掉头就走，决不食言。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 101,
      "line_end": 103
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_gao_zhan_dao",
      "text": "那有这等便宜事，除非你们全体投海，让出三条船来，否则休想有命去见明天的太阳。哼！你们既恃强抢掠，该知道终有这么的一日。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 105,
      "line_end": 107
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_zhan_dao",
      "speaker_name": "高占道",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "给老子住嘴！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 111,
      "line_end": 111
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_zhan_dao",
      "speaker_name": "高占道",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "这叫敬酒不吃吃罚酒，小子给我报上名来。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 111,
      "line_end": 113
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_gao_zhan_dao",
      "text": "老小子你先说！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 115,
      "line_end": 115
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_zhan_dao",
      "speaker_name": "高占道",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "一个小子，一个老小子，这倒公平，听着了，老子就是东海三义之首'双枪'高占道。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 117,
      "line_end": 119
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_gao_zhan_dao",
      "text": "幸好你用的兵器特别点，若是用剑，岂非要唤作'单剑'高占道，这外号定是你自己起的，对吗？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 121,
      "line_end": 123
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_zhan_dao",
      "speaker_name": "高占道",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "胡说八道，你既不肯罢休，就唤你的同伙出来，大家一决高下。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 127,
      "line_end": 129
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_gao_zhan_dao",
      "text": "要收拾你们这些小贼，那用得到我兄弟出手。高占道你若还有点贼胆，就和我单打独斗，只要能捱过十招，本少爷立即放人。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 133,
      "line_end": 137
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_zhan_dao",
      "speaker_name": "高占道",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "闭嘴！我高占道岂容你左一句小贼右一句小贼的乱叫，也不甚么十招之数，就让我们手底下见个真章吧。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 139,
      "line_end": 141
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_gao_zhan_dao",
      "text": "你们登船抢掠，不是贼是甚么？恃强凌弱，只敢向没有抵抗力的渔民百姓下手，不是小贼又是那码子的东西？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 143,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_zhan_dao_shou_xia",
      "speaker_name": "高占道手下",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你不也是贼吗？偷运私盐算甚么正经勾当？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 149,
      "line_end": 151
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有甚么不正经的，西北需盐，我等不辞劳苦，万水千山将盐运去，明卖明买，双方心甘情愿，岂不胜于夺人血汗辛苦赚回来的钱货吗？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 153,
      "line_end": 155
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "男儿立身于世，至紧要立志远大，放眼天下。老子赚了这笔钱后，就用来招兵买马，转战天下，成万世不朽的大业，你这群只懂左抢右夺的小贼怎能明白。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 159,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_zhan_dao",
      "speaker_name": "高占道",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "废话！让老子秤秤你有多少斤两。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 165,
      "line_end": 167
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_gao_zhan_dao",
      "text": "既能挡我一刀，今赵的事就此作罢。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 185,
      "line_end": 185
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_zhan_dao",
      "speaker_name": "高占道",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "阁下高姓大名？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 187,
      "line_end": 189
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_gao_zhan_dao",
      "text": "我叫寇仲，我的兄弟叫徐子陵，你们未听过绝不出奇。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 191,
      "line_end": 193
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_zhan_dao",
      "speaker_name": "高占道",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "怎会没听过？你们刚烧了海沙帮的十多条船，连李密都奈何不了你们。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 197,
      "line_end": 199
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们的消息倒灵通，是否在登岸逛窑子时听回来的呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 201,
      "line_end": 201
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_dao_jing_ya",
      "speaker_name": "海盗",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "寇爷怎会连这些都可猜到？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 205,
      "line_end": 205
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "让我们来作个交易，我们放回你们五位兄弟，你们就负责弄一席丰富的酒菜来给我两兄弟享用，此后各走各路，如何？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 207,
      "line_end": 209
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_zhan_dao",
      "speaker_name": "高占道",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "像寇爷这种天生的英雄人物，我高占道仍是生平第一趟遇上。寇爷肯不怪我们鲁莽，我们当然是恭敬不如从命了。哈！真痛快！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 211,
      "line_end": 215
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_gao_zhan_dao",
      "text": "高兄你们这样下去，终不是办法，可有想过改邪归正？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_feng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "牛奉义",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "现在天下四分五裂，何处才是安居乐业之所。现我们聚众成党，等闲谁都不敢来惹我们，风光得很，就算我们想收手，下面那班兄弟都不肯答应呢。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 249
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zha_jie",
      "speaker_name": "查杰",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "我们只是被迫落草，所以除非迫不得已，否则绝不会胡乱杀人，抢起来亦留有分寸，绝不对穷苦渔民下手，徐爷不信可一问这附近的人，就知我们'东海帮'的行事作风。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "魏元",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "初时我们见两位爷儿打着海沙帮的旗帜，还以为是海沙帮为沈法兴运货的肥羊。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_zhan_dao",
      "speaker_name": "高占道",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "寇爷刚才提及有志争雄天下，不知心中有何大计呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "告诉我，现在谁是最有机会及资格得天下的人？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_zhan_dao",
      "speaker_name": "高占道",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "自然是……嘿！我只是以事论事。若论声威，当然以李密居首。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他只是表面风光。最大的问题是东都城高墙厚，又集中了旧隋精锐的部队，兼之由文韬武略均有两下子的王世充率领，李密以前攻不下洛阳，现在更攻不下洛阳，一个不小心还要吃败仗呢。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zha_jie",
      "speaker_name": "查杰",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "据传密公精通史学，熟赞《史记》《汉书》，又精于兵法，这可从他屡战屡胜证实此事。且最厉害是他懂得收买人心，若他不能得天下，谁人有此资格。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 283
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "别忘了还有窦建德在东北方牵制着李密。何况李密这家伙千不该万不该，做了一件最不做的事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 289
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_feng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "牛奉义",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "甚么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就是杀了大龙头翟让，便以前跟随翟让的旧将人人不满和自危，瓦岗军再非以前团结一致的瓦岗军了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_zhan_dao",
      "speaker_name": "高占道",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "可是现在万众归心，天下群雄纷纷往荥阳依附密公，图成大业，实力该是有增无减。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这恰好做成两个大问题，首先是旧人怕给新人排挤，更添上曾与翟让关系密切的一众将领的疑虑；其次本是精锐的瓦岗军会因此变得良莠不齐，其中更说不定渗进了各方派去的奸细。哼！人说李密如何才具超卓，照我看只不过尔尔，若我是他，只会软禁翟让，让他做个有名无实的傀儡首领。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 308
    }
  ],
